 * Listeners will be called with the following arguments:
 * <ul>

 *       <li>
 *           <code>this_:ext.grid.ColumnModel</code>

 *       </li>

 *       <li>
 *           <code>columnIndex:Number</code>
 The column index
 *       </li>

 *       <li>
 *           <code>newWidth:Number</code>
 The new width
 *       </li>

